Description:
------------
Dance Team The Smurfs mixtures of the charts songs with classical melodies in more than 20 dances for fun, all created by professional choreographers and directed by the legendary blue characters.
Dance party in the Smurfs, the children and parents can dance with their favorite characters and heroes of the film, including Smurfette, Papa Smurf, clumsy, intelligent, brave and Gargamel. Players can enjoy moving to a wide variety of musical genres including pop, R & B, Rock and Punk. Each track is unique and capable choreography for four dancers in Party Mode
